The paper discusses the development of a tool for data visualization, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (HC), information retrieval (IR), database systems (DB), artificial intelligence (AI), and social and information networks (SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.HC, followed by cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.AI, and cs.SI.
